<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00060</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING A SOCIALIZED MICROFINANCING PROGRAM FOR MICRO ENTERPRISES THEREBY PROMOTING ENTREPRENEURSHIP</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : "Pondo Sa Pagbabago At Pagasenso" Or The "P3 Act"
Provides for a socialized microfinancing program for micro enterprises thru the creation of the Pondo sa Pagbabago at Pagasenso (P3) which shall be lent to qualified MSMEs under such terms and conditions that will meet the purposes of this Act.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>YAP, VICTOR A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. De Venecia (000 2019-08-28)</td><td>2. Vergara (000 2019-09-12)</td><tr><td>3. Nieto (000 2019-09-26)</td><td>4. Agabas (000 2019-11-13)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON MICRO, SMALL AND MEDIUM ENTERPRISE DEVELOPMENT ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>